{"tid":1543201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"幫完人之後講「光復香港 時代革命」？","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:37.000Z","uid":302364,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d2438f88ac55dcf8457c940094a42809306f7d0b","tid":1543201,"uid":302364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早幾日搭車，見到個阿婆好慘咁企喺度。我就讓座比佢啦，佢都好開心好感恩地多謝我。<br />\n之後佢坐低咗攞部手機出嚟，我一望：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街又係啲hihi藍絲page!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 佢望住示威者嘅眼神同望我好唔同，真係好似望緊暴徒咁，充滿住嫌棄同不屑。嗰下真係又嬲又無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n件事證明咗，政府一直嘅文宣真係對一啲蠢人好有效，啲廢老完全妖魔化曬我哋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果我地每人做完一件好事/幫完人之後講返句「光復香港 時代革命」</span></span>，就可以令到示威者喺教育程度低嘅市民心目中嘅形象改變，達到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「去妖魔化」</span></span>嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n依個方法無論和理非定勇武都可以幫手！<br />\n幫推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"80594996aa99043fe1ccc06a6237cf063d421554","tid":1543201,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.